  %p
    The US Go Congress is the largest Go tournament in the United States.
    It happens once a year and spans one week. Events include:
  %p
    %span.event-title US Open - 
    the largest annual Go tournament in the US
  %p
    %span.event-title North American Ing Masters -
    16 of the strongest amateur and professional players in North America
  %p
    %span.event-title The Redmond Cup -
    the preeminent youth tournament of the year
  %p
    = link_to "Pro lectures, Simuls,", vip_attendees_path
    Vendor area

  %div{:style => "clear:left;"}

- if @contents.size > 0
  %h3 Announcements

- @contents.each do |c|
  %h4
    = c.created_at.to_date.to_formatted_s(:long)
    \-
    = c.subject
  = Markdown.new(c.body).to_html.html_safe
